sub_title: Senior Executive at Produce Monitoring Board | Co-founder and CEO at Weli Agrolink SL Ltd
summary:
Experienced Senior Executive with a demonstrated history of working in the agricultural marketing, research and produce monitoring industry. Skilled in Sales, Leadership, Customer Service, Produce Quality Assessment and Data Analysis. 
A vibrant business development professional graduated from University of Sierra Leone, and have two MBA degrees.
A change maker with a committed focus in eradicating poverty, eliminating hunger and fighting inequality through agriculture in rural communities in Sierra Leone.
Over 7 year experience working in the intersection between agriculture, gender equality and rural development through facilitation of training on good agricultural practices, provision of improved seeds, organic fertilizer and tools, and enhancing access to farm finance to the most vulnerable.
